title: STULZ Clima Unit: Alerts
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/environment/stulz
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This plug-in checks all connected clima units on a stulz management for an alert state.
 If the state not equal to zero, {CRIT} will be returned. No configuration is needed.

item:
 The bus and the unit number, e.g. {{2-1}}

discovery:
 One service is created for each device.
